'''Asset Tracking''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] military intelligence office operating under the jurisdiction of [[New Republic Fleet Intelligence]]. It was invaluable in the [[Black Fleet Crisis]], discovering the [[Yevetha]]n [[Black Fleet]], which posed a significant threat to the security of the New Republic. Analysts, bureaucrats, and other officials considered Asset Tracking to be a dead-end or career-ending posting and often managed to transfer to other offices; by [[16 ABY/Legends|16]] and [[17 ABY/Legends|17 ABY]], its director and sole member was [[Ayddar Nylykerka]].

